text: Xiangyang Subdistrict () is a subdistrict in Qinghe District, Tieling, Liaoning, China. , it has five residential communities, one village, and one industrial park community under its administration. == See also == * List of township-level divisions of Liaoning == References == Category:Township-level divisions of Liaoning Category:Qinghe District, Tieling
